      "text": [
        " طَلَاقُ الْمَمْلُوكِ لِلْحُرَّةِ ثَلَاثُ تَطْلِيقَاتٍ وَ طَلَاقُ الْحُرِّ لِلْأَمَةِ تَطْلِيقَتَانِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Humeyd Bin Ziyad, from Ibn Sama’at, from Muhammad Bin Ziyad, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘A divorce of the owned slave to the free woman are three divorces, and a divorce of the free man to the slave woman are two divorces’."
        ]
      }
